@sicarul For future reference, your commit message needs to be prefixed with the JIRA id (i.e. [AIRFLOW-547]), so that the JIRA id appear in the release notes. We pull commit subject lines in order to build release notes. 

It's not critical for this trivial update to the companies list, but is a practice for our contributors. More info here https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/AIRFLOW/Contributors%27+Guide

Typically, our merge tool catches this, but I need to manually merge this morning and missed it. Cheers!

